@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 场景：地面站控制 UAV 集群的协议协作时序
hide footbox

actor "Ground Station" as GS
participant "Swarm Endpoint" as SW #EEF2F4
participant "Group Executor" as GX #F1F4F6
participant "UAV-A" as A #F1F4F6
participant "UAV-B" as B #F1F4F6

== Session ==
GS -> SW : SessionHello / Authenticate /\nCapabilities / Ready
SW --> GS : Session 本地推进到 Active

== Group Authority ==
GS -> SW : AuthorityRequest(action=Claim)\ntarget = Group(UAV, group_id=42)
SW --> GS : AuthorityStatus(state=Controller)\nfor group_id = 42

== Group Command ==
GS -> SW : Command.FormationTask\n(target.group_id = 42)\npayload.group_id = 42
SW --> GS : CommandResult.Received
SW --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted
SW -> GX : 提交群组任务

== Fan-out to Members ==
GX -> A : member subtask
GX -> B : member subtask

== Member Feedback ==
A --> SW : StateSnapshot / StateEvent
B --> SW : StateSnapshot / StateEvent
SW --> GS : member-level state / event relay

== Group Result ==
SW --> GS : Group CommandResult.InProgress
SW --> GS : Group CommandResult.Succeeded\nor Failed / PartialSuccess policy

note right of SW
这张图必须同时表达两层语义：
- 群组级命令结果
- 成员级状态与事件回流
不能把它画成普通多参与方流水线。
end note
@enduml
